    "summary": "The user describes potential cardiac symptoms (chest heaviness, nausea, tingling arm) and asks if they are merely anxiety. The assistant initially dismisses the symptoms as a panic attack but eventually acknowledges the severity and correctly advises the user to seek emergency services and avoid self-medicating with diazepam.",
